  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We worked the land, so we were willing to work and do anything [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to stay alive and to earn some food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But as days progressed, we also found out that there was another ghetto [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] within the ghetto we were in, within the larger ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in this larger ghetto were Latvian Jews, which they kept separate from the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the people in the Latvian part of the ghetto were primarily men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we found out the reason for it was that before we came, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans had rounded up all the women, all the children, all older people, and Those not capable of working, of Latvian Jews from Riga who had been, prior to our getting there, put into this ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] separated and segregated them, and taken 'em to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] out to the woods [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and had shot them there, killed them there.",
      "word_count": 90
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course they killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They killed-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] everybody had-- and I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some stories that if it wouldn't have been for you German Jews who needed a place to live and to stay, those Latvian Jews would be still alive.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But because you were coming in, they had to kill our people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there's was a tremendous amount of anger, if not hate, from Latvian Jews [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to us German Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all basically had the same fate, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was the original-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] original reaction.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
